=pl-kos>.</span><span class=pl-c1>lg</span><span class=pl-kos>}</span></span>)`</span><span class=pl-kos>,</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js-L33\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"33\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js-LC33\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=pl-c1>xl</span>: <span class=pl-s>`@media (min-width: <span class=pl-s1><span class=pl-kos>${</span><span class=pl-s1>sizes</span><span class=pl-kos>.</span><span class=pl-c1>xl</span><span class=pl-kos>}</span></span>)`</span><span class=pl-kos>,</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js-L34\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"34\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js-LC34\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=pl-c1>max</span>: <span class=pl-s>`<span class=pl-s1><span class=pl-kos>${</span><span class=pl-s1>sizes</span><span class=pl-kos>.</span><span class=pl-c1>xlg</span><span class=pl-kos>}</span></span>`</span><span class=pl-kos>,</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js-L35\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"35\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js-LC35\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=pl-kos>}</span><span class=pl-kos>;</span></td>\n      </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n  </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gist-meta\">\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/willmendesneto/fc4b5537f3712e3bd3d2e32f4731dacb/raw/3856bb4c1d762e3ed2aeec94ca7d968272c8d820/css-in-js-breakpoints.js\" style=\"float:right\">view raw</a>\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/willmendesneto/fc4b5537f3712e3bd3d2e32f4731dacb#file-css-in-js-breakpoints-js\">css-in-js-breakpoints.js</a>\n        hosted with &#10084; by <a href=\"https://github.com\">GitHub</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div></p>\n<h2>The results</h2>\n<p>As a final result, your app will have a single place as the source of your breakpoints, without any needs of matchMedia listeners and other complex API's at the first step, unless they're really needed. </p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/609ff/website-media-queries.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/fb34c/website-media-queries.avif 320w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/646cd/website-media-queries.avif 768w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/8b485/website-media-queries.avif 1024w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/a73d6/website-media-queries.avif 1280w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/76846/website-media-queries.avif 1500w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/cb523/website-media-queries.webp 320w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/cd067/website-media-queries.webp 768w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/53334/website-media-queries.webp 1024w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/4b075/website-media-queries.webp 1280w,\n/static/582ccf2503a1339775697566e9516edc/4004c/website-media-queries.webp 1500w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw